== Overview ==

Dragon Warrior III features 106 unique monsters across both the Light World and Dark World. This page documents monster stats and battle behaviors.

== Monster Data Structure ==

Each monster entry is 16 bytes:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00 || 1 || Strength
|-
| $01 || 1 || Agility
|-
| $02-$03 || 2 || HP
|-
| $04 || 1 || Defense
|-
| $05 || 1 || Attack pattern
|-
| $06 || 1 || Spell pattern
|-
| $07 || 1 || Magic resistance
|-
| $08 || 1 || Sleep resistance
|-
| $09 || 1 || Stopspell resistance
|-
| $0A-$0B || 2 || Experience
|-
| $0C-$0D || 2 || Gold
|-
| $0E || 1 || Drop item ID
|-
| $0F || 1 || Drop rate (1/X)
|}

